Package exe.bbllw8.either

Class Failure<T>

java.lang.Object
exe.bbllw8.either.Try<T>
exe.bbllw8.either.Failure<T>
public final class Failure<T> extends Try<T>
A failure that occurred during a computation wrapped in a Try type. Holds a Throwable object that represents the failure point.

Note: instances of the following classes are not handled:

  • LinkageError
  • VirtualMachineError
Since:
3.0.0
